  TEMP_MS5611 * 9 / 5 + 32 AS TEMP_MS5611_F, 
  TEMP_BMP388 * 9 / 5 + 32 AS TEMP_BMP388_F, 
  TEMP_TMP117 * 9 / 5 + 32 AS TEMP_TMP117_F
